{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after the war, they were not a girlfriend or boy-- but they just, you know, they-- when they saw each other, something there developed, a feeling.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after the war, they got married in November, '46.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we all moved to Heidenheim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was, again, there was like a suburb, you can say, in Heidenheim.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were only Jewish people, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know how-- how we always have curfew, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we lived all together, my sister-in-law, my brother-in-law, the two of us, and my-- and somebody else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all lived in the same place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you establish a-- a religious life, again, in Heidenheim?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think that the other people around me were not really very keen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that they still had to work on themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think I always-- I always sort of went in this direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I just did my bit, regardless, if I heard from people around me, you know, that they-- that-- why this has happened, why that had happened.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where was-- I don't even-- I can't even say it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't say it, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So where was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And where was the-- where was the strength from above?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where was this, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I always said that it is I-- I-- that faith is a part of me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a living-- it's a-- it always was like a little candle within me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody asked me when I would-- people like myself, it was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a part of you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where did you go from Heidenheim?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Heidenheim, we decided to-- so we were going, really, between Heidenheim and Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We decided to go with Aliyah Bet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Aliyah Bet is illegally-- there was no legal way.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
